Interface StartupInformationListener

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface StartupInformationListener
This interface describes a startup information listener. There are separate startup information listeners for StartupInformationListener.Ibm3270 and StartupInformationListener.Ibm5250.
